    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been assessed or flagged with documented epistemic gap justifications consistent with MRL 5 requirements. The assessment is accepted as a complete credibility evaluation package demonstrating that the CFD hemolysis model does not currently meet the required credibility levels for Class III VAD regulatory submission. The structured gap analysis, including the mechanistic basis for shear-induced RBC damage thresholds reviewed in the methods literature (see referencesIdentifier), provides a defensible roadmap for future model improvement activities.",
